c: 7
v: 11
t: "And We brought you into being by a special creation, and We fashioned you and gave you form and countenance and made you a determinate exalted being. Then We said to the augels: \"Prostrate yourselves to Adam -your archetype- in adoration\" and the angels prostrated in comely order, praise and adoration, except Iblis who aspersed with calumny and declined"